`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIT Delhi receives heavy inbound for CS/AI/communications labs; acceptance there can dip below 10% for unsolicited emails. Less crowded areas (textiles, some civil sub-domains) are relatively more accessible if you present direct relevance. Funding availability and lab bandwidth influence final numbers each year."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:n.jsx(e.strong,{children:"Avoid these blockers:"})}),`
`,n.jsxs(e.ul,{children:[`
`,n.jsx(e.li,{children:"Generic CV blasts without lab-specific anchoring."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.li,{children:'Overpromising (e.g., "will deliver a published paper") without a realistic plan for 68 weeks.'}),`
