`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"NIT Surathkal operates in Surathkal, Karnataka, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning Ocean and coastal engineering, Computer science and systems, Power and energy and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across top public tech institutes, anchor your choices with labs, facilities, and sponsored work rather than brand alone."}),`
