`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Popular AI/data/robotics labs are heavily contested; unsolicited acceptance can fall below 10%. Niche domains (e.g., Civil and structures) may be more accessible if you present direct alignment. Funding availability shifts acceptance dynamicssponsored projects prefer interns who can commit fully on campus."}),`
